title: Counter-Strike Latest version by Valve. Rip from Steam!
description:
-------------============++++++++ENGLISH++++++++============------------

This is the latest version by Valve.

Content:
1. Avatar image in the left side of each player on score tab.
2. Shows Steam players avatars on score tab.
3. Working Internet Browser.

Faq:

Q: Player says that he have Steam but no avatar.
R: Unfortunately is a game bug. If you have 640X480 resolution, you cannot see Steam users avatar on score tab and nobody can see your avatar.

Q: I get an error asking for DLL-s.
RL Install the latest Visual C++ Redistributable Package X86 (even if you are X64)

For any problems, leave a comment.

P.S. Seed, people, seed! I have only 100 GB bandwidth on host!

-------------============++++++++ROMANA++++++++============------------

Aceasta este ultima versiune scoasa de Valve.

Contine:
1. Avar in stanga fiecarui jucator in fereastra cu scor.
2. Arata avatarul tuturor jucatorilor care au steam (inlocuieste avatarul default).
3. Internet Browser functional.

Faq:

Q: Jucatorul spune ca are Steam dar nu are avatar.
R: Din nefericire acesta este un bug al jocului. Jucatorul care are rezolutia 640X480 nu are avatarele in lista cu scor si nici alt utilizator nu ii vede avatarul. Pentru a afla daca un jucator are Steam sau nu, scrie "status" in consola si uita-te la Steam ID.

Q: Imi cere DLL-uri pentru a rula jocul.
R: Instaleaza Visual C++ Redistributable Package X86 (chiar daca ai X64)
Pentru orice problema, lasa un comentariu.

P.S. Tineti la donare ca am doar 100 GB banda pe host!
